The tract of land herein reserved shall be non-alienable and shall not be subject to occupation, entry, sale, lease or other modes of disposition until again declared as alienable and disposable through proclamation.

IN WITNESS WHEREOF, I have hereunto set my hand and caused the seal of the Republic of the Philippines to be affixed.

Done in the City of Manila this 10 th day of September, in the year of Our Lord, Two Thousand and Nine.

(Sgd.) GLORIA MACAPAGAL-ARROYO

By the President:

Executive Secretary
